/****************************/
What is dispatcher servlet?
the job of the DispatcherServlet is to take an incoming URI and find the right combination of 
handlers (generally methods on Controller classes) and views (generally JSPs) that combine to
 form the page or resource that's supposed to be found at that location.
 
Whos is configuring dispatcher servlet?
spring boot configuration

What does dispatcher servlet do?

How does the hello world objetc get converted to JSON
spring boot configuration

Who is configuring the erro mapping?

/******/
@Component: Indica que esa clase va a la base de datos
@RequestBody : Annotation indicating a method parameter should be bound to the body of the HTTP request.
@Autowired: Marks a constructor, field, setter method or config method as to be autowired by Spring's dependency injection facilities.
Revisar> http://programandoointentandolo.com/2013/05/inyeccion-de-dependencias-en-spring.html